(66, '587760e06da07', 1, 50, 'EMERGINC POMEGRANATE GEL CLEANSER 2366', 'EmerginC', 'EmerginC Pomegranate Gel Cleanser', 'A clean-rinsing, fresh-scented gel cleanser with fruit and plant extracts to clean the skin without drying.\r\n\r\nSkin Types: All skin types.\r\n\r\nResults: Thoroughly cleanses and removes excess oil without drying.\r\n', 'local', '', 'uploads/2017-01-12/ca061d15e2c253ff9fabe0719ade47ac.jpeg', 225.00, 225.00, '240 ml', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Directions ', 'Ingrediants', '', '', '', '', 'Morning and/or night, apply on wet skin, add water as needed to create lather, rinse thoroughly.', 'Water, Sodium Lauryl Glucose Carboxylate , Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Lauryl Glucoside, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate Cocoglucoside, Glyceryl Oleate, Urea, Chamomilla Recutita (Matricaria) Extract, Punica Granatum (Pomegranate) Extract, Citrus medica Limonum (Lemon) Peel Extract, Rubus Fruticosus (Blackberry) Fruit Extract, Camellia Sinensis (Green Tea) Leaf Extract, Glycyrrhiza Glabria (Licorice) Root Extract, Arnica Montano Flower Extract, Echinacea Angustifolia (Coneflower) Leaf Extract, Glucononlactone, Sodium Benzoate, PEG/PPG 120/10 Trimethylolpropane Triolate, Caramel.', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, '2017-01-12 16:56:32', '2017-01-15 08:29:29'),
