(106, '5877e5b548132', 1, 57, 'EmerginC Complexion Perfection', 'EmerginC', 'EmerginC Complexion Perfection', 'An instant skin transformation serum with potent concentrations of Alpha-Lipoic Acid, retinol and Siberian sea buckthorn extract. Alpha-Lipoic Acid is known as the "master-antioxidant" for its ability not only neutralize free radicals itself, but also to revitalize other, "spent" antioxidants so that they can continue to neutralize free-radicals. Alpha-Lipoic Acid is one of the only known antioxidants that is both water and lipid soluble for unique effectiveness.\r\n\r\nSea buckthorn extract contains some of the highest concentrations in nature of tocopherols (Vitamin E), carotinoids (Vitamin A), Vitamin C, minerals, bioflavanoids, lipids, tallows and more, to instantly improve skin tone and texture. Skin is left feeling incredibly silky and radiant.\r\n\r\nBenefits:\r\n•Instantly smoothes and firms skin\r\n•Energizes and nourishes skin\r\n•Fights free radical damage\r\n•Helps increase cellular turnover\r\n•Leaves skin silky and glowing\r\n•Ideal for all skin types\r\n', 'international', '', 'uploads/2017-01-12/825281788360f423c8a0064f62635d63.jpeg', 296.00, 296.00, '10 ml', NULL, NULL, 'uploads/2017-01-12/825281788360f423c8a0064f62635d63.jpeg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Directions', 'Ingrediants', '', '', '', '', 'Use morning and/or night. Apply a few drops by itself, or blend in with your favorite EmerginC cream.', 'Vegetable Oil, Squalane, Cyclopentasiloxane, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Retinyl Palmitate (Vitamin A), Retinol, Dimethicone, Tocopheryl Acetate (Vitamin E), Camellia Sinensis (Green Tea) Oil, Thioctic Acid (Alpha Lipoic Acid), Hippophae Rhamnoides (Seabuckthorn) Oil', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, '2017-01-13 02:23:17', '2017-01-13 02:23:17'),
